fields.name: DeletionDate
fields.description: UTC Timestamp when the service was soft-deleted. The date conforms to the following format: yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

fields.name: ScheduledPurgeDate
fields.description: UTC Date and Time when the service will be automatically purged. The date conforms to the following format: yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

fields.name: ServiceId
fields.description: Fully-qualified API Management Service Resource ID
